      <data key="d8">WIND VELOCITY</data>
      <data key="d9">COMPLEMENTS</data>
      <data key="d10">Ventilation strategies and increased wind velocity together provide greater reduction in airborne pathogen concentration than either alone, especially in large or complex indoor spaces.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">e45568c3-e22e-4830-92f5-64de955e8aee_chunk_7</data>
