      <data key="d8">COMMUTER BUS</data>
      <data key="d9">APPLIED_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">Ventilation strategies are applied to commuter buses to reduce airborne transmission risk, as validated by computational and field studies.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.6</data>
