      <data key="d7">ASHRAE/ASHE STANDARD 170-2008: VENTILATION OF HEALTH CARE FACILITIES</data>
      <data key="d8">ASHRAE HANDBOOK-FUNDAMENTALS</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">ASHRAE/ASHE Standard 170-2008 is validated by the technical principles and data provided in the ASHRAE Handbook-Fundamentals, ensuring that the ventilation requirements for healthcare facilities are based on established engineering knowledge.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b_chunk_6</data>
      <data key="d14">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="ASHRAE/ASHE STANDARD 170-2008: VENTILATION OF HEALTH CARE FACILITIES" target="ASHRAE RISK MANAGEMENT GUIDANCE FOR HEALTH, SAFETY AND ENVIRONMENTAL SECURITY UNDER EXTRAORDINARY INCIDENTS">
      <data key="d7">ASHRAE/ASHE STANDARD 170-2008: VENTILATION OF HEALTH CARE FACILITIES</data>
      <data key="d8">ASHRAE RISK MANAGEMENT GUIDANCE FOR HEALTH, SAFETY AND ENVIRONMENTAL SECURITY UNDER EXTRAORDINARY INCIDENTS</data>
      <data key="d9">COMPLEMENTS</data>
      <data key="d10">ASHRAE/ASHE Standard 170-2008 complements the ASHRAE Risk Management Guidance by providing specific ventilation standards that operationalize the broader risk management strategies recommended in the guidance document.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.6</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b_chunk_6</data>
      <data key="d14">3fc1e87d-c54a-447e-9229-2850cf6a1b9b</data>
    </edge>
