      <data key="d9">APPLIED_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">ASHRAE/ASHE Standard 170-2008 specifies the requirements and parameters for the application of ventilation as an engineering control in healthcare facilities.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.8</data>
